The R40 between Hazyview and Bushbuckridge has been closed as a result of a protest.A truck has been pulled over the road, blocking all traffic.Hazyview Police Station confirmed the protest. Motorists have been warned to make use of alternative routes. ALSO READ: Murder in suburbia: elderly man killed while thieves make off with laptop and TV The reason for the protest is not yet clear.This is a developing story. Hazyview Herald will update the public as soon as information becomes available.